Review_body:
I will begin with what I liked at this movie:
-Margot Robbie played very well;
-Ewan McGregor was alright;
-The fight scenes were good;But the script was awful, the intrigue came out of nowhere, the jokes weren t funny at all (and this comes from a guy that laughs at almost any joke in a movie), and also I didn t like the way they presented the story, it was confusingIn conclusion, not really a bad movie but was it is more the kind of "girls night movie" and I would have wanted something different from a story about one of my favourites DC characters
